{"tid":1771472,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救]樓上夜晚好撚嘈 點搞","createTime":"2019-12-06T01:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T02:48:46.000Z","uid":57168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ecf001d842bed76bd15f65b58dae47e5f3c1b52d","tid":1771472,"uid":57168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T01:44:59.000Z","msg":"琴晚由12點開始聽到樓上有人講野<br />\n唔係傾計果種講 係好似得佢一個人咁講野<br />\n直程聽到佢每人句講乜 <br />\n但我住咁耐 都未試過聽到咁應聲<br />\n利申非公屋<br />\n但正常人聲會咁應聲？ <br />\n我已經關曬窗 但都聽到佢講 <br />\n佢把聲就好似隔住d野咁係咁講 <br />\n仲要好激動 <br />\n我開頭以為自己幻聽 點知我全家都聽到<br />\n屋企人已經成日訓唔好 成日失眠<br />\n而家有埋呢d聲仲訓得唔好<br />\n<br />\n可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a95ab161e67f701759d5c7eef7a7a761e70611c","tid":1771472,"uid":57168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T01:45:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"473c23c9da2b2315d60dc016c4fe1f25dc29d76f","tid":1771472,"uid":57168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T01:45:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22c4deca991762b4c0d51f4798c086a990b13c0b","tid":1771472,"uid":57168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T01:47:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cca5ae255e31e9a7fc92fad3f2c335e25ae64ae","tid":1771472,"uid":210707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T01:47:46.000Z","msg":"會唔會撞鬼...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a8fc61ccc9d0e7fdd2ca143c11f64fb426d478","tid":1771472,"uid":190781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite